tooltip.rtsurvival.renderScale: Sets the scale used for rendering waypoints
tooltip.rtsurvival.fullWaypointNames: Toggles whether waypoint names are concise or full
tooltip.rtsurvival.highlightHoveredWaypo: Toggles whether closest waypoint is highlighted
tooltip.rtsurvival.crossDimensionalWaypo: Displays overworld waypoints in the Nether
tooltip.rtsurvival.waypointColor: Sets the color of the waypoints
tooltip.rtsurvival.waypointTransparency: Sets the transparency of the waypoints
tooltip.rtsurvival.highlightWaypointColo: Sets the color of the highlighted waypoint
tooltip.rtsurvival.highlightWaypointTran: Sets the transparency of the highlighted waypoint
tooltip.rtsurvival.distanceBackgroundCol: Sets the color of the distance background
tooltip.rtsurvival.distanceBackgroundTra: Sets the transparency of the distance background
tooltip.rtsurvival.waypoints.keybindings: Contains the keybindings related to waypoints
